doc.after: Paul Skalich 1534 1573 also known as Stanislav Pavao Skali or Paulus Scalichius de Lika was an encyclopedist Renaissance humanist and adventurer born in Zagreb Croatia and who lived part of his life in Germany 1 His surname is rendered in various other ways e g in English Skalich Scalich Scaliger in Latin Scalichius or Scaligius and in Spanish Scalitzius
